You need to **put any JS and CSS files inside `src`**, otherwise Webpack won\rquote t see them.\par
\par
Only files inside `public` can be used from `public/index.html`.<br>\par
Read instructions below for using assets from JavaScript and HTML.\par
\par
You can, however, create more top-level directories.<br>\par
They will not be included in the production build so you can use them for things like documentation.\par
